        "content": "<p>I started to implement the OCR-A font as an exercise with creating sketches. Here is two renderings of OCR-A's numbers:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/-oKKWGo3Zf034NaqJX7MOPtO/OCR-Plastic-NUMs.png\">OCR-Plastic-NUMs.png</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/bkvPQZNJzgYDek7DHIf4PP5N/OCR-NUMs.png\">OCR-NUMs.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/-oKKWGo3Zf034NaqJX7MOPtO/OCR-Plastic-NUMs.png\" title=\"OCR-Plastic-NUMs.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"5000x5000\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/1549/-oKKWGo3Zf034NaqJX7MOPtO/OCR-Plastic-NUMs.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/bkvPQZNJzgYDek7DHIf4PP5N/OCR-NUMs.png\" title=\"OCR-NUMs.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"5000x5000\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/1549/bkvPQZNJzgYDek7DHIf4PP5N/OCR-NUMs.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><p>And finally a screengrab for a more precise view:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/Pt_s-A7z-tnIrdQn8AlqHw-N/screengrab-OCR-A-Nums.png\">screengrab-OCR-A-Nums.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/Pt_s-A7z-tnIrdQn8AlqHw-N/screengrab-OCR-A-Nums.png\" title=\"screengrab-OCR-A-Nums.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"722x1041\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/1549/Pt_s-A7z-tnIrdQn8AlqHw-N/screengrab-OCR-A-Nums.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><p>I will probably finish the entire font set in a week or so.</p>\n<p>If you want to peruse the OCR-A specificaion NIST published it on their website: (<a href=\"https://nvlpubs.nist.gov/nistpubs/Legacy/FIPS/fipspub32-1-1981.pdf\">https://nvlpubs.nist.gov/nistpubs/Legacy/FIPS/fipspub32-1-1981.pdf</a>)</p>",
        "id": 483022601,
        "sender_full_name": "Benjamin Fennell",
        "timestamp": 1731936565
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It took longer than expected. But I have gotten some letters done.</p>\n<p>Here are two BRL-CAD renderings in the OCR-A font:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/xzxik9ThYQqQzUJdWkrIG9Ek/BRL-CAD2.png\">BRL-CAD2.png</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/Z2HPMwIgc0LXMsC4kQae1fp3/BRL-CAD1.png\">BRL-CAD1.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/xzxik9ThYQqQzUJdWkrIG9Ek/BRL-CAD2.png\" title=\"BRL-CAD2.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"2000x2000\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/1549/xzxik9ThYQqQzUJdWkrIG9Ek/BRL-CAD2.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/Z2HPMwIgc0LXMsC4kQae1fp3/BRL-CAD1.png\" title=\"BRL-CAD1.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"2000x2000\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/1549/Z2HPMwIgc0LXMsC4kQae1fp3/BRL-CAD1.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
