        "content": "<p>I made a quick animation of it, but for some reason the extrusions were flashing in and out. It still looks kinda cool though:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/sBqYh7r7tKfvgLs4nzv60cw6/BRL3.webm\">BRL3.webm</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image message_inline_video\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/sBqYh7r7tKfvgLs4nzv60cw6/BRL3.webm\" title=\"BRL3.webm\"><video preload=\"metadata\" src=\"/user_uploads/1549/sBqYh7r7tKfvgLs4nzv60cw6/BRL3.webm\"></video></a></div>",
